{
  "stem": "142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when the gas-- they get very, very tight, and-- and it takes a long-- a lot of force to be able to drag the bodies from-- from the gas chambers, you know, to put it in the elevator going on the second floor, and then, you know, in stretchers, and in the ovens.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were enough people there to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were about 100, I think, in-- in ours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- there were 1,200 people all together in the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With the bunkers, we're here, we're there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, we were 100 in mine-- 100 or 150, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it takes 400 to 600, and the others were around for other things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- we-- we had enough personnel, but, you know, we were working shifts also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You needed more people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were 35 Greeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the end, I think, we were left only 26, I think-- more or less.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We will go to the-- just you put them in the ovens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two other people, you know, that putting in stretchers, three, four of them in stretchers, and put 'em in the oven.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And actually, they had to take-- put the outside, the women inside the men, because the women have more fat that can-- could burn the-- the bodies.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You put about four.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think, were-- in each crematorium were eight ovens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "20 to 30 minutes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, then you know, they take the ashes out, and they-- you pulverize the ashes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they get taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The trucks come and take 'em to the Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the kapos on the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we had only one or two guards there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't too many SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're always outside the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
